EVALUATE
	ROW(
	"Emission_moyenne", 'Fact_DPE'[Emission moyenne]
)

DEFINE
	VAR __DM3FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"84"}, 'Dim_Geo'[code_region_ban])

	VAR __DM5FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({("84", "1")}, 'Dim_Geo'[code_region_ban], 'Dim_Geo'[code_departement_ban])

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			ROLLUPADDISSUBTOTAL(
				'Dim_Geo'[code_region_ban], "IsGrandTotalRowTotal",
				'Dim_Geo'[code_departement_ban], "IsDM1Total", NONVISUAL(__DM3FilterTable),
				'Dim_Geo'[nom_commune_ban],
				"IsDM3Total",
				NONVISUAL(__DM3FilterTable),
				NONVISUAL(__DM5FilterTable)
			),
			"Sumconso_5_usages_ef_energie_n1", CALCULATE(SUM('Fact_DPE'[conso_5 usages_ef_energie_n1]))
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(
			502,
			__DS0Core,
			[IsGrandTotalRowTotal],
			0,
			'Dim_Geo'[code_region_ban],
			1,
			[IsDM1Total],
			0,
			'Dim_Geo'[code_departement_ban],
			1,
			[IsDM3Total],
			0,
			'Dim_Geo'[nom_commune_ban],
			1
		)

EVALUATE
	__DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
	[IsGrandTotalRowTotal] DESC,
	'Dim_Geo'[code_region_ban],
	[IsDM1Total] DESC,
	'Dim_Geo'[code_departement_ban],
	[IsDM3Total] DESC,
	'Dim_Geo'[nom_commune_ban]

DEFINE
	COLUMN '__SQDS0VisualCalcs'[Calcul] = 
		(/* USER DAX BEGIN */
BLANK()
/* USER DAX END */)

	VAR __SQDS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			ROLLUPADDISSUBTOTAL('Dim_Geo'[code_postal_ban], "IsSQDS0GrandTotalRowTotal"),
			"Nb_DPE", 'Fact_DPE'[Nb DPE]
		)

	VAR __SQDS0VisualCalcsInput = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(
				SELECTCOLUMNS(
					__SQDS0Core,
					"code_postal_ban", 'Dim_Geo'[code_postal_ban],
					"IsSQDS0GrandTotalRowTotal", [IsSQDS0GrandTotalRowTotal],
					"Nb_DPE", [Nb_DPE]
				)
			),
			"code_postal_ban", [code_postal_ban],
			"IsSQDS0GrandTotalRowTotal", [IsSQDS0GrandTotalRowTotal],
			"Nb DPE", [Nb_DPE]
		)

	TABLE '__SQDS0VisualCalcs' = 
		__SQDS0VisualCalcsInput
		WITH VISUAL SHAPE
			AXIS rows
				GROUP [code_postal_ban] TOTAL [IsSQDS0GrandTotalRowTotal]
				ORDER BY
					[code_postal_ban] ASC
			DENSIFY "IsDensifiedRow"

	VAR __SQDS0RemoveEmptyDensified = 
		FILTER(
			KEEPFILTERS('__SQDS0VisualCalcs'),
			OR(
				NOT('__SQDS0VisualCalcs'[IsDensifiedRow]),
				NOT(ISBLANK('__SQDS0VisualCalcs'[Calcul]))
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(
				FILTER(
					KEEPFILTERS(__SQDS0RemoveEmptyDensified),
					'__SQDS0VisualCalcs'[IsSQDS0GrandTotalRowTotal] = FALSE
				)
			),
			"'__SQDS0VisualCalcs'[code_postal_ban]", '__SQDS0VisualCalcs'[code_postal_ban],
			"'__SQDS0VisualCalcs'[Nb DPE]", '__SQDS0VisualCalcs'[Nb DPE],
			"'__SQDS0VisualCalcs'[Calcul]", '__SQDS0VisualCalcs'[Calcul]
		)

	VAR __DS0RemoveContextOnlyColumns = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core),
			"'__SQDS0VisualCalcs'[code_postal_ban]", '__SQDS0VisualCalcs'[code_postal_ban],
			"'__SQDS0VisualCalcs'[Nb DPE]", '__SQDS0VisualCalcs'[Nb DPE]
		)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		TOPN(
			30002,
			__DS0RemoveContextOnlyColumns,
			'__SQDS0VisualCalcs'[Nb DPE],
			0,
			'__SQDS0VisualCalcs'[code_postal_ban],
			1
		)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	'__SQDS0VisualCalcs'[Nb DPE] DESC, '__SQDS0VisualCalcs'[code_postal_ban]

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		VALUES('Fact_DPE'[etiquette_dpe])

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed =
